{"tid":2084792,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"終於個孫未出世可以睇到猁拎英超","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:04:35.000Z","uid":53396,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29e27309141561c19b0ad945154b68d742dec903","tid":2084792,"uid":53396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"我真係好感動垃圾猁終於拎到30年第一冠<br />\n獌笑9咗猁咁耐終於唔可以再抽無英超<br />\n等咁9耐成30年呀大佬幾多猁迷等唔切<br />\n死猁狗呢排一定好撚招積就緊㗎啦<br />\n算啦佢哋到依家屈咗咁耐<br />\n9年前贏咗獌聯爭簽嘅軒達臣竟然威過謝4<br />\n數返呢10年迷失咗咁耐嘅猁狗係值得加許<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a286c677c90d6444ca47a2004087303949aa22","tid":2084792,"uid":266467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45NmCKk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45NmCKk.gif&h=72998246&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yof7yhG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyof7yhG.gif&h=5957a793&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WA0WrCH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWA0WrCH.gif&h=b4c6517f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCCxKpo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCCxKpo.gif&h=a87b7292&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uFGCKp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uFGCKp.gif&h=3b00ef66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6cmCKr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6cmCKr.gif&h=8991bb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WyEpps.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WyEpps.gif&h=d98a9efb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://n